metadata.name: Deadly Woman
metadata.description:
It seems our friendly neighbor Ned Flanderukama has found himself in quite a bind. Could this be Ned's final diddly?  
Find out next time on - MARGE: Assassin

In an alternate reality, Marge Simpsonaru is a sword-wielding assassin on a blood soaked mission to avenge her family, leaving a trail of bodies as she cuts her way through the deadly streets of Springjuku.

1/1
